title: Honest Trailers Puts a Hit Out on 'John Wick'
text:
Screengrab via ScreenJunkies/YouTube BTW 
Just in time for the premiere of John Wick 2 , the folks over at Honest Trailers are roasting the movie that started it all. 
John Wick , an action thriller starring Keanu Reeves, became an unexpected cult hit back in 2014. That's because the plot is pretty much just a retired hitman running around and murdering people after somebody killed his dog. Oh, and there's a secret society of assassins. It's revenge flick fun at its finest. It's true Reeves doesn't have the best luck with his action movie sequels, but here's hoping John Wick 2 is just as badass as the original.
